reviewText: When I purchased this video I also purchased a couple of other 20/20 videos. I though that, at least this would be around 30 minutes. There was no time length identified. So imagine my surprise when I found out the video was all of ten minutes and no more. I paid $15 for 10 minutes of video? I think that this was misrepresented by Amazon by NOT listing the length. I intend to contact Amazon.com about this. I would not waste my money on this.
